column5: While i was stoped for breakfast this morning in Bancroft i notice some one gasing up their fancy boat at the pumps , both the tow vehicle and the boat were decaled  up with thease words " EXTREME ANGLER " and EXTREME TV  , Any one know who this guy was ??????????????????
Karl Kalonka? He likes to fish Baptiste.
You just described the Skipper.........  Harold

That was him then . I was busy chucking down my breakfast at Rosa's when i notice him out side gasing up at the pumps so i did'nt get a chance to have a conversation with him , by the time i came out to leave he  was gone . I did find out tho that we share the same taste in out likes for our boat color being Black  ...... lol . If you's ever hear he's looking for his double to do stunts or any thing send me a PM right away , i just might be able to help him out . Thanks again Fella's
I miss Rosa's breakfast! Spent many long weekends camping at riverbend and going for big breakfast at Rosa's
Sounds like half the fishing boats I see going up the 400.  All stickered up...  I hope they are getting paid by all those advertisers, lol!
